column5: Got a bunch of small pike and whitefish this evening as well as 4 walleye, this beastiewaited to the very last minute , I was reeling up to pack away when it shot off bottom and nailed a 1/16Oz  jig and small minnow I was using for whitefish…26”…back she went.
Nice  I love pulling in big fish
I nearly lost it at the hole, was worth getting a wet arm for the picture…. Lol.
LOL  wet arms really suck but they make it interesting
